%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Project Manager

participant UI as WBS Ownership UI
participant BFF as Execution BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant EXE as Execution Service
participant RMS as Resource Management Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

PM->>UI: Open WBS item for owner assignment
UI->>BFF: Load eligible owners
BFF->>ORCH: Get tagged resources for project
ORCH->>RMS: Fetch approved project allocations
RMS->>READDB: Query active resource allocations
READDB-->>RMS: Tagged resources
RMS-->>ORCH: Eligible owners
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show owner dropdown

PM->>UI: Select owner and Save
UI->>BFF: Assign WBS owner
BFF->>ORCH: Start owner assignment flow
ORCH->>EXE: Save WBS owner
EXE->>PRIMARYDB: Insert/Update WBS execution owner mapping
PRIMARYDB-->>EXE: Save success
EXE-->>ORCH: Save success
ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish WBSOwnerAssigned Event
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Show updated owner